'''Aradian pulse-lifters''' were an [[Atmosphere/Legends|atmospheric]] drive system. Developed around [[15 ABY/Legends|15 ABY]], pulse-lifters were an alternative to the commonly used [[Repulsorlift/Legends|repulsorlifts]]. The pulse-lifters created massive shockwaves and sonic disruptions, preventing their use in high-traffic areas. They were sufficiently rare to draw the interest of [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] military officials when used on [[Yevetha]]n [[Aramadia-class thrustship|''Aramadia''-class thrustships]].

